text: Doris Kirkman (July 15, 1930 - June 16, 2010) was an American gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2010 deaths Category:American female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Elizabeth, New Jersey
